Rulings.Edison:
●The Ignition Effect activates & resolves on the field.
●This effect targets 1 Dragon-Type monster in your opponent’s GY.
●This effect is negated by Necrovalley.
●The Continuous Effect applies while this card is face-up on the field.
●If you control two copies of Victoria, your opponent can't attack your Fairy-Type monsters.
Rulings.Tengu:
(1) Once per turn, you can select and Special Summon 1 Dragon-Type monster in your opponent's GY to your side of the field. (2) Your opponent cannot select another face-up Fairy-Type monster as an attack target.
●The (1) Ignition Effect activates & resolves on the field.
●This effect targets 1 Dragon-Type monster in your opponent’s GY.
●This effect is negated by Necrovalley.
●The (2) Continuous Effect applies while this card is face-up on the field.
●If you control two copies of Victoria, your opponent cannot attack your Fairy-Type monsters.
